snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls Online: Welcome to Shadows of the Hist
snippet.description:
Introducing the Cradle of Shadows and Ruins of Mazzatun, two new four-player dungeons included with the Shadows of the Hist DLC game pack – out now for PC/Mac, Xbox One, & PlayStation®4!

http://www.elderscrollsonline.com/en-us/dlc/shadowsofthehist

For more information about The Elder Scrolls Online, visit our website: http://www.elderscrollsonline.com/

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/ElderScrollsOnline/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/TESOnline 
instagram: https://instagram.com/elderscrollsonline
Google+: https://plus.google.com/+ElderScrollsOnline/

ESRB Rating: MATURE with Blood and Gore, Sexual Themes, Use of Alcohol, and Violence
